{
  "id": "RAW_180043ee",
  "title": "阿里升级千问：超级 Agent，开始接管超级 App",
  "url": "https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s?__biz=MTMwNDMwODQ0MQ==&mid=2653097256&idx=1&sn=890c7ea60e10c5cf8329013a069c089b",
  "date": "2026-01-15 13:04:00",
  "author": "极客公园",
  "siteName": "极客公园",
  "content": "<html>\n <head></head>\n <body>\n  <div data-mpa-template=\"t\" mpa-paragraph-type=\"ignored\">\n   <div mpa-from-tpl=\"t\" mpa-paragraph-type=\"ignored\" data-pm-slice=\"3 5 []\">\n    <p style=\"margin-left:8px;letter-spacing:1px;clear:both;font-size:16px;min-height:1em;margin-bottom:0em;margin-right:8px;text-align:center;\" mpa-from-tpl=\"t\"><span leaf=\"\"><img data-aistatus=\"1\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.66640625\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"jpeg\" data-w=\"1280\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color:transparent;vertical-align:bottom;width:100%;font-size:14px;text-align:left;\" data-croporisrc=\"https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_jpg/8cu01Kavc5bUT5gF2ZuNlXAq7z9mg7T93Bt3sexOlicE3fAKfSHFM8hnXynVo72FzZEBUGTtfm56Y1fkMGIzMNQ/0?wx_fmt=jpeg&amp;from=appmsg\" data-cropselx2=\"562\" data-cropsely2=\"341\" data-backw=\"562\" data-backh=\"375\" data-imgfileid=\"505613603\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=189ad26d&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_jpg%2F8cu01Kavc5bUT5gF2ZuNlXAq7z9mg7T93Bt3sexOlicE3fAKfSHFM8hnXynVo72FzZEBUGTtfm56Y1fkMGIzMNQ%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Djpeg%26from%3Dappmsg\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-src=\"\"></span></p>\n    <p style=\"padding:25px 18px 18px;margin:-0.6em 8px 2em;background-size:100%;letter-spacing:0.3px;clear:both;font-size:15px;min-height:1em;line-height:1.8em;background-position:100% 100%;background-color:rgb(0, 0, 0) !important;background-repeat:no-repeat;text-align:justify;\" mpa-from-tpl=\"t\"><span mpa-font-style=\"mkffs8gk108m\" style=\"font-family: Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;\"><span leaf=\"\">AI 时代的核心战场，正在从争夺流量入口，变成抢占「意图」入口。</span></span></p>\n    <p style=\"margin-left:8px;text-indent:0em;letter-spacing:1px;clear:both;font-size:17px;margin-top:25px;min-height:1em;line-height:1.5em;margin-right:8px;text-align:left;\" mpa-from-tpl=\"t\"><strong mpa-from-tpl=\"t\" style=\"text-indent:0em;font-size:16px;font-family:Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;\" mpa-font-style=\"mkffs8gkjdd\"><span leaf=\"\">作者｜苏子华</span></strong></p>\n    <p style=\"margin-left:8px;text-indent:0em;letter-spacing:1px;clear:both;font-size:17px;min-height:1em;line-height:1.5em;margin-right:8px;text-align:left;\" mpa-from-tpl=\"t\"><strong mpa-from-tpl=\"t\" style=\"text-indent:0em;font-size:16px;font-family:Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;\" mpa-font-style=\"mkffs8gksh3\"><span leaf=\"\">编辑｜</span><strong mpa-from-tpl=\"t\"><span leaf=\"\">郑玄</span></strong></strong></p>\n   </div>\n  </div>\n  <p style=\"margin:48px 8px 25px;letter-spacing:1px;font-size:16px;line-height:1.75;text-align:justify;\" mpa-paragraph-type=\"body\"><span leaf=\"\" mpa-font-style=\"mkffs8gk1dq8\" style=\"font-family: Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;\">阿里在争夺 AI 时代的超级入口方面，又搞了一个大动作。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin:25px 8px;letter-spacing:1px;font-size:16px;line-height:1.75;text-align:justify;\" mpa-paragraph-type=\"body\"><span leaf=\"\" mpa-font-style=\"mkffs8gkk0p\" style=\"font-family: Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;\">1 月 15 日，阿里旗下的千问在杭州召开了产品发布会，核心就是两个事：</span></p>\n  <ul style=\"list-style-type: disc;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\" class=\"list-paddingleft-1\">\n   <li>\n    <p style=\"letter-spacing:1px;font-size:16px;margin-top:25px;line-height:1.75;margin-bottom:25px;text-align:justify;\" mpa-paragraph-type=\"body\"><span leaf=\"\" mpa-font-style=\"mkffs8gk1ksj\" style=\"font-family: Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;\">千问 App 全面接入淘宝、支付宝、淘宝闪购、飞猪、高德等阿里生态业务。相当于把整个阿里都装进了千问 App；</span></p>\n   </li>\n  </ul>\n  <ul style=\"list-style-type: disc;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\" class=\"list-paddingleft-1\">\n   <li>\n    <p style=\"letter-spacing:1px;font-size:16px;margin-top:25px;line-height:1.75;margin-bottom:25px;text-align:justify;\" mpa-paragraph-type=\"body\"><span leaf=\"\" mpa-font-style=\"mkffs8gk1j02\" style=\"font-family: Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;\">推出千问任务助理 1.0 版本。用户更新千问 App 客户端后即可申请参加邀测，随后几天内将全面开放免费使用。该助理可以执行应用开发、办公软件操作、学习辅导等任务。</span></p>\n   </li>\n  </ul>\n  <p style=\"margin:25px 8px;letter-spacing:1px;font-size:16px;line-height:1.75;text-align:justify;\" mpa-paragraph-type=\"body\"><span leaf=\"\" mpa-font-style=\"mkffs8gkdr6\" style=\"font-family: Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;\">这一次产品升级，终于让千问 App 与豆包、元宝、ChatGPT 等 AI 助手产品有了真正的差别。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin:25px 8px;letter-spacing:1px;font-size:16px;line-height:1.75;text-align:justify;\" mpa-paragraph-type=\"body\"><span leaf=\"\" mpa-font-style=\"mkffs8gk1i6b\" style=\"font-family: Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;\">千问 App 是阿里在 2025 年 11 月推出的 AI 助手。上线 23 天，月活用户数突破 3000 万；如今上线 2 个月，月活用户数已经突破 1 亿。成为近期增长最快的 AI 应用之一。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin:25px 8px;letter-spacing:1px;font-size:16px;line-height:1.75;text-align:justify;\" mpa-paragraph-type=\"body\"><span leaf=\"\" mpa-font-style=\"mkffs8gk1pk5\" style=\"font-family: Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;\">如果回看最早期版本，千问并不独特。它的 App 页面和豆包、元宝们高度相似。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin:25px 8px 8px;letter-spacing:1px;font-size:16px;line-height:1.75;text-align:justify;\" mpa-paragraph-type=\"image\"><span leaf=\"\"><img data-aistatus=\"1\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.66650390625\" data-w=\"4096\" style=\"width: 100%;\" data-backw=\"578\" data-backh=\"385\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=6f12cb7c&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_jpg%2F8cu01Kavc5bUT5gF2ZuNlXAq7z9mg7T96vAjvBSRwlF1vQwY6VnLpuuEib5HdbLXyVviaov4KxXJH6wdlqApRR3A%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Djpeg%26from%3Dappmsg\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-src=\"\"></span></p>\n  <div data-mpa-template=\"t\" mpa-paragraph-type=\"secondTitle\">\n   <div mpa-from-tpl=\"t\">\n    <p style=\"margin-left:8px;letter-spacing:1px;font-size:16px;line-height:1em;text-align:justify;margin-right:8px;\" mpa-paragraph-type=\"body\" data-pm-slice=\"3 2 []\"><strong style=\"text-align: left;color: rgb(255, 47, 0);font-family: Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;\" mpa-from-tpl=\"t\" mpa-font-style=\"mkffs8gk1rq3\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"color: rgb(178, 178, 178);font-weight: normal;\">千问 App 发布会现场｜图片来源：极客公园</span></span></strong></p>\n   </div>\n  </div>\n  <p style=\"margin:25px 8px;letter-spacing:1px;font-size:16px;line-height:1.75;text-align:justify;\" mpa-paragraph-type=\"body\"><span leaf=\"\" mpa-font-style=\"mkffs8gk1cpq\" style=\"font-family: Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;\">但阿里对千问 App 赋予了极高的期待。据了解，阿里为此进行了一次资源大整合。过去一段时间，千问团队一直在「封闭」开发，其团队不仅有来自夸克的产研人员，还有大量从高德、淘宝、支付宝等核心部门紧急抽调的员工。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin:25px 8px;letter-spacing:1px;font-size:16px;line-height:1.75;text-align:justify;\" mpa-paragraph-type=\"body\"><span leaf=\"\" mpa-font-style=\"mkffs8gk8nv\" style=\"font-family: Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;\">而更值得关注的，是升级后的千问 App，正在变为一个超级 Agent。这个超级 Agent 正在接管超级 App。阿里的逻辑很清晰：把整个阿里生态的各种生活服务，全部装进千问，统一交给 AI 来调度。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin:25px 8px;letter-spacing:1px;font-size:16px;line-height:1.75;text-align:justify;\" mpa-paragraph-type=\"body\"><span leaf=\"\" mpa-font-style=\"mkffs8gk3rt\" style=\"font-family: Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;\">Agent 变成前台，App 在向后退。这时，不难看出来，互联网的入口逻辑，已经变了。</span></p>\n  <div data-mpa-template=\"t\" mpa-paragraph-type=\"title\">\n   <div data-mpa-template=\"t\" mpa-data-temp-power-by=\"yiban.io\" data-mpa-action-id=\"mkffnyws1u4g\" data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\">\n    <div data-mpa-template=\"t\" mpa-from-tpl=\"t\">\n     <div style=\"margin-left:8px;letter-spacing:0.578px;font-size:16px;margin-right:8px;text-align:justify;\" mpa-from-tpl=\"t\">\n      <div style=\"margin-top: 10px;text-align: center;justify-content: center;display: flex;flex-flow: row;\" mpa-from-tpl=\"t\">\n       <div style=\"display: inline-block;width: auto;vertical-align: top;min-width: 10%;height: auto;flex: 0 0 auto;align-self: flex-start;\" mpa-from-tpl=\"t\">\n        <div style=\"isolation: isolate;\" mpa-from-tpl=\"t\">\n         <div style=\"font-size: 36px;line-height: 1;letter-spacing: 0px;color: rgb(45, 113, 214);\" mpa-from-tpl=\"t\">\n          <p style=\"clear: both;min-height: 1em;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span style=\"font-family: Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;\" mpa-font-style=\"mkffs8gkwmi\"><em><strong mpa-from-tpl=\"t\"><span leaf=\"\">01</span></strong></em></span></p>\n         </div>\n        </div>\n       </div>\n      </div>\n     </div>\n     <p mpa-from-tpl=\"t\" style=\"text-align: center;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><strong style=\"letter-spacing:0.578px;font-size:17px;font-family:Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;\" mpa-from-tpl=\"t\" mpa-font-style=\"mkffs8gkm6c\"><span style=\"\" mpa-is-content=\"t\"><span leaf=\"\" data-pm-slice=\"1 1 [&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;section&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{&quot;data-mpa-template&quot;:&quot;t&quot;,&quot;mpa-paragraph-type&quot;:&quot;title&quot;},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;},&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;section&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{&quot;mpa-from-tpl&quot;:&quot;t&quot;},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;},&quot;node&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;strong&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{&quot;style&quot;:&quot;color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9); font-size: 17px; letter-spacing: 0.578px; text-align: center;&quot;,&quot;mpa-from-tpl&quot;:&quot;t&quot;},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;},&quot;node&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;span&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{&quot;style&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;mpa-is-content&quot;:&quot;t&quot;},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;}]\">超级 Agent 正在接管 App</span></span></strong></p>\n    </div>\n   </div>\n  </div>\n  <p style=\"margin:25px 8px;letter-spacing:1px;font-size:16px;line-height:1.75;text-align:justify;\" mpa-paragraph-type=\"body\"><span leaf=\"\" mpa-font-style=\"mkffs8gk1w1r\" style=\"font-family: Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;\">现在的千问和豆包，虽然还叫 App，但叫它们「超级 Agent」或许更合适。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin:25px 8px;letter-spacing:1px;font-size:16px;line-height:1.75;text-align:justify;\" mpa-paragraph-type=\"body\"><span leaf=\"\" mpa-font-style=\"mkffs8gk1742\" style=\"font-family: Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;\">回想一下，当淘宝 App 里整合了淘宝闪购，我当时就卸载了饿了么，转而在淘宝里点外卖；当淘宝也整合了飞猪后，我也卸载了飞猪。一个超级淘宝 App，满足了各种消费需求。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin:25px 8px;letter-spacing:1px;font-size:16px;line-height:1.75;text-align:justify;\" mpa-paragraph-type=\"body\"><span leaf=\"\" mpa-font-style=\"mkffs8gk24hr\" style=\"font-family: Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;\">现在的超级 Agent 正在重演这一幕。千问 App 变成了那个承载各种服务的超级入口，各个 App 变成了幕后的「工具包」。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin:25px 8px;letter-spacing:1px;font-size:16px;line-height:1.75;text-align:justify;\" mpa-paragraph-type=\"body\"><span leaf=\"\" mpa-font-style=\"mkffs8gk10sh\" style=\"font-family: Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;\">这时，用户不再需要记住办这件事用哪个 App，只需要表达意图即可。例如，据千问 C 端事业群总裁吴嘉现场介绍：</span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin:25px 8px;letter-spacing:1px;font-size:16px;line-height:1.75;text-align:justify;\" mpa-paragraph-type=\"body\"><span leaf=\"\" mpa-font-style=\"mkffs8gk19hk\" style=\"font-family: Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;\">在生活服务上，千问已经接入支付宝政务能力，上线了签证、户口、公积金等 50 项民生服务。用户不再需要在不同部门官网之间来回跳转，只要一句「杭州户口怎么办护照」，千问就能完成政策解读、材料清单整理，并直接跳转到办理入口。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin:25px 8px 8px;letter-spacing:1px;font-size:16px;line-height:1.75;text-align:justify;\" mpa-paragraph-type=\"image\"><span leaf=\"\"><img data-aistatus=\"1\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.6663740122914837\" data-w=\"2278\" style=\"width: 100%;\" data-backw=\"578\" data-backh=\"385\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=560984a3&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_jpg%2F8cu01Kavc5bUT5gF2ZuNlXAq7z9mg7T9ZmibWXYh5fXWxNk2WGlRI7e84PkAIhGEdxsp9j8txdGJZXJk6vPgQrw%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Djpeg%26from%3Dappmsg\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-src=\"\"></span></p>\n  <div data-mpa-template=\"t\" mpa-paragraph-type=\"secondTitle\">\n   <div mpa-from-tpl=\"t\">\n    <p style=\"margin-left:8px;letter-spacing:1px;font-size:16px;line-height:1em;text-align:justify;margin-right:8px;\" mpa-paragraph-type=\"body\" data-pm-slice=\"3 2 []\"><strong style=\"text-align: left;color: rgb(255, 47, 0);font-family: Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;\" mpa-from-tpl=\"t\" mpa-font-style=\"mkffs8gk1lyw\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"color: rgb(178, 178, 178);font-weight: normal;\">这里在展示千问 App 内自如调用支付宝服务的能力｜图片来源：极客公园</span></span></strong></p>\n   </div>\n  </div>\n  <p style=\"margin:25px 8px;letter-spacing:1px;font-size:16px;line-height:1.75;text-align:justify;\" mpa-paragraph-type=\"body\"><span leaf=\"\" mpa-font-style=\"mkffs8gklds\" style=\"font-family: Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;\">在出行场景中，它可以调用飞猪完成机酒预订，调用高德规划行程，甚至在春节场景下，直接帮用户打电话订餐厅。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin:25px 8px;letter-spacing:1px;font-size:16px;line-height:1.75;text-align:justify;\" mpa-paragraph-type=\"image\"><span leaf=\"\"><img data-aistatus=\"1\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.66650390625\" data-w=\"4096\" style=\"width: 100%;\" data-backw=\"578\" data-backh=\"385\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=2a7db0bf&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_jpg%2F8cu01Kavc5bUT5gF2ZuNlXAq7z9mg7T9cPJcJNKnS9ADSibgSUQxUPK470jsge4BcjCnbO8MOouITw0vQ3ibdUGQ%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Djpeg%26from%3Dappmsg\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-src=\"\"></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin:25px 8px 8px;letter-spacing:1px;font-size:16px;line-height:1.75;text-align:justify;\" mpa-paragraph-type=\"image\"><span leaf=\"\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-aistatus=\"1\" data-backh=\"385\" data-backw=\"578\" data-ratio=\"0.66650390625\" style=\"width: 100%;\" data-w=\"4096\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=eaf34ccc&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_jpg%2F8cu01Kavc5bUT5gF2ZuNlXAq7z9mg7T9a25Vma1vpNgiaS567TLrVatDyTFMbpwoUIqhfkSMTW0mdKianga45BDA%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Djpeg%26from%3Dappmsg\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-src=\"\"></span></p>\n  <div data-mpa-template=\"t\" mpa-paragraph-type=\"secondTitle\">\n   <div mpa-from-tpl=\"t\">\n    <p style=\"margin-left:8px;letter-spacing:1px;font-size:16px;line-height:1em;text-align:justify;margin-right:8px;\" mpa-paragraph-type=\"body\" data-pm-slice=\"3 2 []\"><strong style=\"text-align: left;color: rgb(255, 47, 0);font-family: Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;\" mpa-from-tpl=\"t\" mpa-font-style=\"mkffs8gkms7\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"color: rgb(178, 178, 178);font-weight: normal;\">这里在展示千问 App 调用高德、飞猪、支付宝，给用户策划出行攻略的能力｜图片来源：极客公园</span></span></strong></p>\n   </div>\n  </div>\n  <p style=\"margin:25px 8px;letter-spacing:1px;font-size:16px;line-height:1.75;text-align:justify;\" mpa-paragraph-type=\"body\"><span leaf=\"\" mpa-font-style=\"mkffs8gk1vfb\" style=\"font-family: Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;\">只需一句话，剩下的就交给这个超级 Agent。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin:25px 8px;letter-spacing:1px;font-size:16px;line-height:1.75;text-align:justify;\" mpa-paragraph-type=\"body\"><span leaf=\"\" mpa-font-style=\"mkffs8gk1d5j\" style=\"font-family: Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;\">当然，所有这些设想，都有一个前提：模型足够强，尤其是 Coding 能力。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin:25px 8px;letter-spacing:1px;font-size:16px;line-height:1.75;text-align:justify;\" mpa-paragraph-type=\"body\"><span leaf=\"\" mpa-font-style=\"mkffs8gkssq\" style=\"font-family: Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;\">现在的 Agent 要执行复杂任务，本质上是模型在后台实时生成代码、调用 API、处理逻辑。大模型的 Coding 能力越强，它能接管的工具就越多，执行的动作就越精准。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin:25px 8px;letter-spacing:1px;font-size:16px;line-height:1.75;text-align:justify;\" mpa-paragraph-type=\"body\"><span leaf=\"\" mpa-font-style=\"mkffs8gk1mm7\" style=\"font-family: Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;\">千问 C 端事业群总裁吴嘉在发布会上表示，千问之所以能实现「办事能力」的突破，可以归因于三个技术突破：</span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin:25px 8px;letter-spacing:1px;font-size:16px;line-height:1.75;text-align:justify;\" mpa-paragraph-type=\"body\"></p>\n  <ol style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\" class=\"list-paddingleft-1\">\n   <li><strong style=\"letter-spacing:0px;font-size:16px;margin-top:0px;line-height:1.6;font-family:Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;margin-bottom:0px;text-align:left;\" mpa-font-style=\"mkffs8gk11xh\"><span leaf=\"\">Coding 能力的大幅提升：</span></strong>\n    <p><span leaf=\"\" mpa-font-style=\"mkffs8gkak3\" style=\"font-family: Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;\">这让 Agent 能实时构建工具，而不是预设功能。</span></p></li>\n   <li><strong style=\"letter-spacing:0px;font-size:16px;margin-top:0px;line-height:1.6;font-family:Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;margin-bottom:0px;text-align:left;\" mpa-font-style=\"mkffs8gk20k5\"><span leaf=\"\">全模态理解能力：</span></strong>\n    <p><span leaf=\"\" mpa-font-style=\"mkffs8gk1wpx\" style=\"font-family: Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;\">能看懂界面、听懂声音、读懂报表。</span></p></li>\n   <li><strong style=\"letter-spacing:0px;font-size:16px;margin-top:0px;line-height:1.6;font-family:Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;margin-bottom:0px;text-align:left;\" mpa-font-style=\"mkffs8gkmpd\"><span leaf=\"\">超长上下文处理：</span></strong>\n    <p><span leaf=\"\" mpa-font-style=\"mkffs8gk1qx4\" style=\"font-family: Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;\">提升了复杂任务的交付上限。</span></p></li>\n  </ol>\n  <p></p>\n  <p style=\"margin:25px 8px;letter-spacing:1px;font-size:16px;line-height:1.75;text-align:justify;\" mpa-paragraph-type=\"body\"><span leaf=\"\" mpa-font-style=\"mkffs8gk251l\" style=\"font-family: Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;\">在此基础上，千问 App 开始测试「任务助理」功能：具备类人化的多步骤规划能力，覆盖办公、开发、调研、生活办事等多个场景，完成复杂任务。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin:25px 8px;letter-spacing:1px;font-size:16px;line-height:1.75;text-align:justify;\" mpa-paragraph-type=\"body\"><span leaf=\"\" mpa-font-style=\"mkffs8gknqz\" style=\"font-family: Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;\">更重要的是，多位 Agent 创业者曾对极客公园表示，做 Agent 更能够敏锐感知到大模型能力的变化，同时用户使用 Agent 来完成复杂任务时，能够在交互中留下大量的关于意图、行为相关的数据。而这正是互联网上更难获取的数据，这些数据，反过来又会推动模型迭代。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin:25px 8px;letter-spacing:1px;font-size:16px;line-height:1.75;text-align:justify;\" mpa-paragraph-type=\"body\"><span mpa-font-style=\"mkffs8gk5cy\" style=\"font-family: Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;\"><span leaf=\"\">做 C 端应用，不是为了单纯的 DAU，而是为了让大模型在实战中变得更强。这是一个螺旋上升的闭环</span><strong style=\"letter-spacing:0px;font-size:16px;margin-top:0px;line-height:1.6;margin-bottom:0px;text-align:left;\"><span leaf=\"\">。</span></strong><span leaf=\"\">阿里必须跑通这个闭环，才能在底层模型的竞争中保持第一梯队。这也是为什么，大厂们越来越重视 C 端 超级 Agent 的战略价值。</span></span></p>\n  <div data-mpa-template=\"t\" mpa-paragraph-type=\"title\">\n   <div data-mpa-template=\"t\" mpa-data-temp-power-by=\"yiban.io\" data-mpa-action-id=\"mkffq7y41c4c\" data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\">\n    <div data-mpa-template=\"t\" mpa-from-tpl=\"t\">\n     <div style=\"margin-left:8px;letter-spacing:0.578px;font-size:16px;margin-right:8px;text-align:justify;\" mpa-from-tpl=\"t\">\n      <div style=\"margin-top: 10px;text-align: center;justify-content: center;display: flex;flex-flow: row;\" mpa-from-tpl=\"t\">\n       <div style=\"display: inline-block;width: auto;vertical-align: top;min-width: 10%;height: auto;flex: 0 0 auto;align-self: flex-start;\" mpa-from-tpl=\"t\">\n        <div style=\"isolation: isolate;\" mpa-from-tpl=\"t\">\n         <div style=\"font-size: 36px;line-height: 1;letter-spacing: 0px;color: rgb(45, 113, 214);\" mpa-from-tpl=\"t\">\n          <p style=\"clear: both;min-height: 1em;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span style=\"font-family: Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;\" mpa-font-style=\"mkffs8gkxuv\"><em><strong mpa-from-tpl=\"t\"><span leaf=\"\">02</span></strong></em></span></p>\n         </div>\n        </div>\n       </div>\n      </div>\n     </div>\n     <p mpa-from-tpl=\"t\" style=\"text-align: center;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><strong style=\"letter-spacing:0.578px;font-size:17px;font-family:Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;\" mpa-from-tpl=\"t\" mpa-font-style=\"mkffs8gkcnm\"><span style=\"\" mpa-is-content=\"t\"><span leaf=\"\" data-pm-slice=\"1 1 [&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;section&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{&quot;data-mpa-template&quot;:&quot;t&quot;,&quot;mpa-paragraph-type&quot;:&quot;title&quot;},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;},&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;section&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{&quot;mpa-from-tpl&quot;:&quot;t&quot;},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;},&quot;node&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;strong&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{&quot;style&quot;:&quot;color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9); font-size: 17px; letter-spacing: 0.578px; text-align: center;&quot;,&quot;mpa-from-tpl&quot;:&quot;t&quot;},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;},&quot;node&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;span&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{&quot;style&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;mpa-is-content&quot;:&quot;t&quot;},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;}]\">互联网核心战场，从争夺流量，</span></span></strong></p>\n     <p mpa-from-tpl=\"t\" style=\"text-align: center;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><strong style=\"letter-spacing:0.578px;font-size:17px;font-family:Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;\" mpa-from-tpl=\"t\" mpa-font-style=\"mkffs8gk4m3\"><span style=\"\" mpa-is-content=\"t\"><span leaf=\"\" data-pm-slice=\"1 1 [&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;section&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{&quot;data-mpa-template&quot;:&quot;t&quot;,&quot;mpa-paragraph-type&quot;:&quot;title&quot;},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;},&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;section&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{&quot;mpa-from-tpl&quot;:&quot;t&quot;},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;},&quot;node&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;strong&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{&quot;style&quot;:&quot;color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9); font-size: 17px; letter-spacing: 0.578px; text-align: center;&quot;,&quot;mpa-from-tpl&quot;:&quot;t&quot;},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;},&quot;node&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;span&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{&quot;style&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;mpa-is-content&quot;:&quot;t&quot;},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;}]\">变为抢占「用户意图」</span></span></strong></p>\n    </div>\n   </div>\n  </div>\n  <p style=\"margin:25px 8px;letter-spacing:1px;font-size:16px;line-height:1.75;text-align:justify;\" mpa-paragraph-type=\"body\"><span leaf=\"\" mpa-font-style=\"mkffs8gk1oqy\" style=\"font-family: Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;\">可以明显地看到一个趋势：无论是互联网大厂，还是手机厂商，大家都在让自己的主力产品，迅速「Agent 化」，变成一个超级 Agent。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin:25px 8px;letter-spacing:1px;font-size:16px;line-height:1.75;text-align:justify;\" mpa-paragraph-type=\"body\"><span mpa-font-style=\"mkffs8gk13e\" style=\"font-family: Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;\"><span leaf=\"\">PC 时代，入口是浏览器和搜索引擎；移动互联网时代，入口是应用商店和超级 App；而 AI 时代，</span><strong style=\"letter-spacing:0px;font-size:16px;margin-top:0px;line-height:1.6;margin-bottom:0px;text-align:left;\"><span leaf=\"\">意图，正在成为新的入口。</span></strong></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin:25px 8px;letter-spacing:1px;font-size:16px;line-height:1.75;text-align:justify;\" mpa-paragraph-type=\"body\"><span leaf=\"\" mpa-font-style=\"mkffs8gkoft\" style=\"font-family: Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;\">展开来说，意图就是来自用户最终的需求，各个 App 是实现这个需求的 action。比如说，给我规划一个去重庆的旅游攻略（意图），那么可能就会用到飞猪（action）、支付宝（action）、高德（action）。这个时候最重要的是，哪个超级 Agent 能够优先获得用户的意图，那么它就有了支配后续各种 App 的权力。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin:25px 8px;letter-spacing:1px;font-size:16px;line-height:1.75;text-align:justify;\" mpa-paragraph-type=\"body\"><span leaf=\"\" mpa-font-style=\"mkffs8gk147k\" style=\"font-family: Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;\">从这个角度看，豆包做手机，本身就是想通过硬件或许更多的系统权限，获得调取调度更多 App 的能力，来完善自身 Agent 的能力。手机本身，其实也是一个超级 Agent。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin:25px 8px;letter-spacing:1px;font-size:16px;line-height:1.75;text-align:justify;\" mpa-paragraph-type=\"body\"><span leaf=\"\" mpa-font-style=\"mkffs8gk1v2t\" style=\"font-family: Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;\">因此，谁能最先、最准确地成为用户意图的第一个接收者，谁就掌握了服务主导权，谁就有机会成为 AI 时代的超级入口。互联网的核心战场，也正在从过去的争夺流量，变为抢占用户「意图」。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin:25px 8px;letter-spacing:1px;font-size:16px;line-height:1.75;text-align:justify;\" mpa-paragraph-type=\"body\"><span mpa-font-style=\"mkffs8gk1di6\" style=\"font-family: Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;\"><span leaf=\"\">此次千问 App 的升级，已经把一个趋势清晰地摆在了台面上：</span><strong style=\"letter-spacing:0px;font-size:16px;margin-top:0px;line-height:1.6;margin-bottom:0px;text-align:left;\"><span leaf=\"\">一个以「意图」为中心、以 Agent 为载体的新互联网形态，正在形成。它的入口极简，后台极繁。</span></strong></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin:25px 8px;letter-spacing:1px;font-size:16px;line-height:1.75;text-align:justify;\" mpa-paragraph-type=\"body\"><span leaf=\"\" mpa-font-style=\"mkffs8gk15eu\" style=\"font-family: Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;\">不过，对于任何 Agent 来说，要想让 Agent 真正「能办事」，就必须能合法、稳定、低摩擦地调用电商、本地生活、支付、地图、政务等能力。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin:25px 8px;letter-spacing:1px;font-size:16px;line-height:1.75;text-align:justify;\" mpa-paragraph-type=\"body\"><span leaf=\"\" mpa-font-style=\"mkffs8gk1z9x\" style=\"font-family: Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;\">这种生态护城河，是其他竞对短期内难以逾越的鸿沟。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin:25px 8px;letter-spacing:1px;font-size:16px;line-height:1.75;text-align:justify;\" mpa-paragraph-type=\"body\"><span leaf=\"\" mpa-font-style=\"mkffs8gk18qz\" style=\"font-family: Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;\">例如，豆包虽然也在接入汽水音乐、抖音电商、即梦等自家业务，但豆包手机在面对外部系统权限时，常会因为安全栅栏被识别为「风险行为」而拦下。而千问在阿里自家的生态里，调用各种服务不存在被限制的可能。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin:25px 8px;letter-spacing:1px;font-size:16px;line-height:1.75;text-align:justify;\" mpa-paragraph-type=\"body\"><span leaf=\"\" mpa-font-style=\"mkffs8gk1xup\" style=\"font-family: Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;\">这或许会成千问快速追赶豆包的关键。因此，也更容易理解为何阿里愿意举集团之力，将千问 App 打造成一个内嵌于阿里经济体的「特权」Agent。让其成为千问的差异化特色。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin:25px 8px;letter-spacing:1px;font-size:16px;line-height:1.75;text-align:justify;\" mpa-paragraph-type=\"body\"><span leaf=\"\" mpa-font-style=\"mkffs8gkae8\" style=\"font-family: Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;\">AI 已经火热了三年，虽然超级 App 的时代，还没有结束。但超级 Agent 的时代，已经开始了。</span></p>\n </body>\n</html>",
  "aiSummary": "阿里千问 App 升级为“超级 Agent”，深度整合阿里生态服务，旨在通过统一调度和强大的 AI 能力抢占 AI 时代“用户意图”入口。",
  "oneSentenceSummary": "阿里千问 App 升级为“超级 Agent”，深度整合阿里生态服务，旨在通过统一调度和强大的 AI 能力抢占 AI 时代“用户意图”入口。",
  "summary": "文章指出，阿里旗下千问 App 推出升级，全面整合了淘宝、支付宝、飞猪、高德等阿里生态业务，并发布了任务助理 1.0 版本，旨在将千问 App 打造成一个能统一调度阿里生态服务的“超级 Agent”。文章详细阐述了 Agent 如何接管用户意图，通过大模型的 Coding 能力、全模态理解能力和超长上下文处理能力，实现复杂任务的执行，例如政务办理、出行规划等。作者认为，AI 时代的核心战场已从争夺流量转变为抢占“用户意图”入口，Agent 正成为连接用户需求与各类服务的关键。文章还强调了阿里生态体系对千问 Agent 发展的独特优势，即能合法、稳定、低摩擦地调用各项服务。最终，文章预示着一个以“意图”为中心、Agent 为载体的新互联网形态正在形成，并认为大厂对 C 端超级 Agent 的重视旨在通过实战数据推动底层模型迭代。",
  "mainPoints": [
    {
      "point": "阿里千问 App 升级为超级 Agent，全面整合阿里生态服务。",
      "explanation": "千问 App 通过接入淘宝、支付宝、飞猪等业务，转型为具备统一调度能力的超级 Agent，旨在满足用户多样化需求，简化跨应用操作。"
    },
    {
      "point": "AI 时代核心竞争从流量转向用户“意图”入口。",
      "explanation": "文章提出，谁能最先准确捕获并响应用户意图，谁就掌握了服务主导权，将成为 AI 时代的超级入口，Agent 是实现这一目标的关键载体。"
    },
    {
      "point": "Agent 能力基于大模型的 Coding、全模态理解和超长上下文处理。",
      "explanation": "千问 Agent 能执行复杂任务得益于其 Coding 能力的提升，可实时构建工具；全模态理解能力，能处理多源信息；以及超长上下文，保障复杂任务的交付上限。"
    },
